OL,3,C'Devastating cuts' to support for
OL,4,Cadopted children leaving parents
OL,5,Cpetrified
OL,7,FRachel told ITV News Meridian: "We run
OL,8,Fout of funds very soon and I don't
OL,9,Fknow at the moment how we're going to
OL,10,Fcontinue with the therapy, which we
OL,11,Fdesperately need.
OL,13,F"I'm petrified for my son and myself
OL,14,Fand for all the other families."
OL,16,FThe controversial reforms to the
OL,17,FAdoption and Special Guardianship
OL,18,FSupport Fund was the topic of a debate
OL,19,Fin Parliament, called by the member
OL,20,Ffor Mid Sussex.
