OL,3,C'Devastating cuts' to support for
OL,4,Cadopted children leaving parents
OL,5,Cpetrified
OL,7,FLib Dem MP Alison Bennett said: "These
OL,8,Fchildren have had the roughest of
OL,9,Fstarts in life. They often need
OL,10,Ftherapy in order to stay with their
OL,11,Fnew families and without that we run
OL,12,Fthe risk of adoptions breaking down,
OL,13,Fchildren returning to the care system
OL,14,Fand a society that is poorer as a
OL,15,Fresult".
