OL,3,C'Devastating cuts' to support for
OL,4,Cadopted children leaving parents
OL,5,Cpetrified
OL,7,FThe Jigsaw Occupational Therapy centre
OL,8,Fin Burgess Hill works with many
OL,9,Fadopted children. Director Dominic
OL,10,FSimpson said any break in sessions,
OL,11,Fdue to lack of funding, hurts the
OL,12,Ftherapy, with his staff having to
OL,13,F"pick up and start again".
OL,15,FThe Department for Education announced
OL,16,Ftoday that the support fund would
OL,17,Fcontinue for the 2026/27 financial
OL,18,Fyear and then be reviewed.
