OL,3,C'Devastating cuts' to support for
OL,4,Cadopted children leaving parents
OL,5,Cpetrified
OL,7,FChildren's Minister, Janet Daby, said
OL,8,Fin a statement to Parliament: "The
OL,9,Fneed for support is clear, which is
OL,10,Fwhy we are determined to ensure that
OL,11,Feffective services are reaching
OL,12,Fchildren and families as efficiently
OL,13,Fas possible."
OL,15,FMinisters have committed to holding a
OL,16,F"public engagement process" on the
OL,17,Ffuture of the scheme next year.
